Print output of an OSEM Forecast

print.osem.forecast.Rd

Print output of an OSEM Forecast

Usage

# S3 method for class 'osem.forecast'
print(x, plot = TRUE, full_names = FALSE, ...)

Arguments

x

An object of type 'osem.forecast'

plot

Logical. Default = TRUE. Should the osem forecast output be plotted?

full_names

Logical. Default = FALSE. Should the full names of the variables from the dictionary be printed?

...

Further arguments.

Value

A printed summary of the OSEM forecast output, including the forecast horizon, method, and central estimates.
